Insider Activity


Individual




Aleem Gillani



Mr. Aleem Gillani is Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at SunTrust Banks, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at March of Dimes Foundation.
Mr. Gillani was previously employed as Chief Market Risk Officer by The PNC Financial Services Group, Inc., a Principal by BankBoston Corp., and a Principal by FleetBoston Financial Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from York University.



